{
  "texts": [
    "A full list of actions used for this sampling can be found in Extended Data Table 1.",
    "In our work, we sampled nearly 1 billion of such premises in a highly parallelized setting, described in Methods.",
    "Note that we do not make use of any existing theorem premises from human-designed problem sets and sampled the eligible constructions uniformly randomly.",
    "Next we use a symbolic deduction engine on the sampled premises.",
    "The engine quickly deduces new true statements by following forward inference rules as shown in Fig. 3b."
  ]
}